; Coverage for history.cc empty prices map for given time window
; Price exists only in the future, so edge filter returns false
; and conversion cannot happen at the requested time

P 2024/06/01 EUR $1.10

2024/01/15 European Travel
    Expenses:Travel    500 EUR
    Assets:Checking

test bal --market --exchange '$' --now 2024/03/01 Expenses
             500 EUR  Expenses:Travel
end test
